      <title>美国扩大对油轮的制裁以遏制伊朗石油运输</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-20/us-broadens-sanctions-on-tankers-to-squeeze-flows-of-iranian-oil</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国对更多涉嫌参与伊朗石油贸易的油轮和公司实施了制裁，这些石油贸易产生的收入用于支持哈马斯和胡塞武装等德黑兰支持的民兵组织。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-20/us-broadens-sanctions-on-tankers-to-squeeze-flows-of-iranian-oil</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 20 Dec 2024 02:06:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
